strings.Value: "Let us raise a toast to those who fought bravely, and died a glorious death."
"We should honor the memory of those who are no longer with us. Let us raise our goblets."
"The dead don't care what toasts we make."
"I could tell you a few things about this peculiar ritual. But perhaps this time I'd better just join the toast."
"That's right. Here's how we honor the fallen fighters. Not with whining. If I drop dead one day, drink in my honor 'til the mountains shake!"
"Their feats will not be forgotten! I'll make sure of that!"
